    <item>
      <title>索马里警方称海滩酒店袭击事件造成 32 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/urgent-somali-police-say-32-people-died-in-an-attack-on-a-beach-hotel-al-shabab-claimed-responsibility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩加迪沙，索马里（美联社）——索马里警方周六称，前一天晚上在首都摩加迪沙的一家海滨酒店发生的袭击造成 32 人死亡，63 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/urgent-somali-police-say-32-people-died-in-an-attack-on-a-beach-hotel-al-shabab-claimed-responsibility</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 09:04:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>税务警告和骚乱暴露挑战，斯塔默蜜月期结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/starmer-honeymoon-ends-as-tax-warnings-riots-expose-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯尔·斯塔默领导的工党很可能希望，近二十年来首次赢得英国大选能带来至少整个夏天的政治蜜月。但不到一个月的时间，治理一个脆弱国家的挑战迅速驱散了任何挥之不去的兴奋感。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/starmer-honeymoon-ends-as-tax-warnings-riots-expose-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南林郑月娥当选越共中央总书记，誓言继续反腐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/vietnam-party-chief-to-continue-anti-graft-push-reduce-red-tape</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南新任共产党总书记苏林表示，他将“坚决”继续大力开展反腐败运动，同时努力缓解官僚主义瓶颈，以提振经济发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/vietnam-party-chief-to-continue-anti-graft-push-reduce-red-tape</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 04:45:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将在不同日期以新条款与哈里斯进行辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/trump-says-he-s-agreed-with-fox-news-to-debate-harris-on-sept-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党人唐纳德·特朗普表示，他愿意于 9 月 4 日在宾夕法尼亚州的福克斯新闻上与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯进行辩论，尽管目前尚不清楚是否就提案条款征求过这位民主党候选人的意见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/trump-says-he-s-agreed-with-fox-news-to-debate-harris-on-sept-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 03:54:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜金正恩指责韩国就洪水问题进行诽谤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/north-korean-leader-accuses-south-korea-of-a-smear-campaign-over-floods-and-hints-at-rejecting-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社）——朝鲜领导人金正恩指责韩国“垃圾”媒体夸大最近该国西北部洪水造成的死亡人数，玷污了朝鲜的形象，并暗示他将拒绝首尔提供的援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/north-korean-leader-accuses-south-korea-of-a-smear-campaign-over-floods-and-hints-at-rejecting-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 03:13:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国防部长撤销对 9/11 策划者指控的认罪协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/urgent-defense-secretary-overrides-plea-agreement-for-accused-9-11-mastermind-and-two-other-defendants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（美联社）——国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀周五推翻了本周早些时候针对 2001 年 9 月 11 日袭击案主谋及另外两名被告达成的认罪协议，将他们重新定性为死刑案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/urgent-defense-secretary-overrides-plea-agreement-for-accused-9-11-mastermind-and-two-other-defendants</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 00:48:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
