    <item>
      <title>马杜罗指责委内瑞拉反对派策划武装袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-gets-electoral-council-nod-in-bid-to-legitimize-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉政府指责反对派伪造选举记录，声称其候选人击败了总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗，并警告称，据称周六将在被禁领导人玛丽亚·科里娜·马查多呼吁和平示威的地方附近发生武装袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-gets-electoral-council-nod-in-bid-to-legitimize-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 19:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾加强南海前哨十年防御</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/philippines-fortifies-south-china-sea-outpost-to-last-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据四位知情人士透露，菲律宾已对在有争议的南海搁浅的一艘二战时期的舰船进行了大规模增援，增援程度足以使这艘与北京关系紧张的前哨基地至少再维持十年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/philippines-fortifies-south-china-sea-outpost-to-last-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:20:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
